The grind behind the glory 💪🏼
The late nights, the endless prep, the millionth pitch practice (and still forgetting our lines 🙃)… it all led to THIS moment. Walking into the Shark Tank felt surreal, but building this brand? That’s been the real ride. 🎢💛

From small wins to big risks, from doubters to believers—this journey has been everything. And now, we’re about to share it with you. 🦈✨
